title: (Mon Full) Amy's Phone Scam + Raymundo Wants "Brotox" + TV Theme Song Game
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Amy's Phone Scam + Raymundo Wants "Brotox" + TV Theme Song Game
description:
Amy got a notification on her iPhone that she had just won a $1,000 gift card from Apple. Did she fill out the survey and claim the prize? Raymundo wants to get "Brotox" as a way to combat the aging process. Show members compete against one another as they try and guess television theme songs!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
